name: Dune Sea Sabacc
Lore: 'R''kik D''nec remains undefeated in this version of sabacc. Or at least there are no witnesses to the contrary.',
Text: 'Requirements: A Jawa at a Tatooine site. Wild cards (0-7): Sandcrawler sites, Magnetic Suction Tube, Jawa Siesta and Jawa Pack. Clone cards: Tatooine locations, sandcrawlers, Jawa weapons, and Utinni! Stakes: One device or droid with out armor.',
